OverHistory.UPDCommentry:
BOOM BOOM GETS THE BANGLA SKIP!  Jasprit Bumrah bowling to Najmul Hossain Shanto, good length ball, pitching on leg stump, tempts the Bangla skipper into a cross-batted heave. But the change-up is too slick; the bat swings, the ball grazes the edge and takes flight. Up, up it goes, and there’s Arshdeep Singh, patrolling the deep third boundary. He moves with purpose, eyes fixed on the descending prize, and with a composed leap, he clasps the ball to his chest.
